      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZOE'S SECRET (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with four wins and two minors from seven tries. In the money last time at this track (18.55) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 2.5 lengths second. Appeals as a leading chance in this. KIANDO DIVA (7) missed the frame last time when fifth (20.10) at Gunnedah but prior to that had two placings in a row. Has a good record here including nine wins. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Can measure up this time. GREYSYND QUINN (2) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at Gunnedah over 340m behind Ava's Milo (20.15) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at his previous run. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Cannot be taken lightly. DOTTIE KEEPING (6) will need to repeat last run to feature.",
